        </span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-green-100 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Let our experts guide you through the best permanent residency pathway for your profile.
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
        <a href="https://intake.immigratic.com/ma?utm_source=immigratic&utm_medium=website&utm_campaign=pr_page&utm_content=final_assessment" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="px-8 py-4 bg-white text-green-900 font-bold rounded-2xl hover:bg-gray-100 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-2xl">
          Start Free Assessment
        </a>
        <a href="https://try.immigratic.com/meetings/immicare/165?utm_source=immigratic&utm_medium=website&utm_campaign=pr_page&utm_content=final_consultation" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="px-8 py-4 border-2 border-white/30 text-white font-bold rounded-2xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300 backdrop-blur-sm">
          Book Expert Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
